Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.51,0:02:14.93,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}可以听听后面的曲子吗
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.89,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}关于澳大利亚我有很多事想知道
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.89,0:02:21.85,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好想坐在CBR上出去兜风
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.48,Default2,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅小姐
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.48,0:02:28.11,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK 大家的愿望我都实现
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.48,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}等等
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.57,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我家从今天起就忙起来了
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.03,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦 我想起来了
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.66,0:02:35.82,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天开始
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.49,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}有什么事吗
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.20,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}天体观测爱好者们的聚会
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.25,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天天气很好 应该能看得很清楚吧
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.42,0:02:49.09,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}星星什么时候都能看啊
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.09,0:02:50.76,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来很多人吗
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.22,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.34,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明天已经客满了
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.18,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽然客满了 但是床上却一个人都没有
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.18,0:02:57.93,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}要问为何
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.56,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为大家都去看星星了
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.43,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}回答正确
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.06,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}带我一回
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.28,0:03:14.28,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这是去年的客人送来的照片
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.74,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好漂亮
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.45,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}星星还能这么漂亮啊
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.33,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好厉害 马洛
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.87,0:03:28.92,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}星星 其实是有很多颜色和形状的啊
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.38,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好漂亮
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.59,0:03:38.80,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这样美丽的颜色到底是如何藏在漆黑的夜空中呢
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.97,0:03:43.81,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也能找到吗
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.94,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我决定了 爸爸
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.98,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:48.72,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拜托你了
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.77,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那我也来当志愿者吧
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.44,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的吗 利绘
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.82,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}非常的认真哦
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.99,0:03:56.95,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没关系吗
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.07,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么我也要
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.78,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也是
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.78,0:04:03.91,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么明天晚上就拜托了
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.79,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天先回家取得家长的同意吧
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.62,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是的
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.92,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.38,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好幸福
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.71,0:04:17.34,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}头阵差不多到了吧
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.09,Default2,Mother and Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.22,Default2,Guest,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}又来打扰您了
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.22,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.68,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}欢迎来到NIWA旅馆
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.44,Default2,Guest,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新来的打工的？
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.94,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是的 请多指教
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.65,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来来来 房间在这边
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.19,0:04:33.90,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}比起客人 更希望能多陪陪我
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.65,0:04:33.90,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.23,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那你住下来不就行了
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.36,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个 小杏 能让我听听后面的曲子吗
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.58,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么了 打算来唱了吗
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.45,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 我想试试看...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.25,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃前辈
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.37,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}终于做好走向世界的觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.92,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽然不是那样的说
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.38,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前辈真的好可爱
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.05,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}稍微等等
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.88,0:04:59.18,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和辛西娅一起去过海边后 有什么不同了呢
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.14,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无所谓啦 你要春乃愿意来唱歌的话
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.14,0:05:02.43,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}给
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.64,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽然我不知道能不能唱好
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.85,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一定没问题的
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.75,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你觉不觉得她比平时还认真
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.42,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.96,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}歌词已经写好了吗
