Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.15,0:05:56.82,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}词曲歌都有了 这组合不就结成了嘛
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.73,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}组合！？
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.94,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是啊
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.82,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}现役高中女生组合
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.32,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}乐队吗 很不错的样子
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.58,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也是啊
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.24,0:06:10.46,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么了怎么了 辛西娅的影响吗
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.08,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们需要起个组合名
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.29,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁知道呢
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.75,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}组合名字就叫[汪汪]
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.09,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不要
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.30,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}随便摆一下就好了
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.30,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK
