Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是小菜一碟吧
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.10,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 sorry
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.48,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好期待春乃你们的组合
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.56,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是吗
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.82,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好想赶快听听你的歌
