Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.32,0:06:44.95,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会？
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.74,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没错
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.33,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}歌曲做好了后会举办的吧
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.95,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃我爱你！
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.04,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.34,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢大家前来捧场
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么 请听我们的新曲
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曲目[未定]
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.89,0:07:13.02,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} 我的家在山上
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.27,0:07:21.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} 养了很多鸡哦
