Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.08,0:07:35.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}呃 因为 还没那个水平
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.83,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你要好好地练习的话 没问题的
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}别说得那么简单
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.63,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.59,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}要办吗
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.55,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不要
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.05,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.51,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}都说了
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.26,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.22,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不办啦
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.18,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.18,0:07:53.93,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可能
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.57,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}并不是不可能哦
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.45,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能去往任何地方的说
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.45,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}非洲？南极也能吗？
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.16,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}能去 能去
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.79,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我爸爸这样告诉我的
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.25,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.04,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是真的哦
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.25,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真的那样的话 好厉害
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.92,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}然后大家一起去很多的地方看看吧
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.13,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大家
