Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.05,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一起去
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.94,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}感觉好像还差一点点
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.94,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小夜呢
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.11,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}同问
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.77,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没问题的啦
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.07,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一定能上红白歌会的
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.07,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}红白歌会？
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.07,0:08:50.36,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}然后渐渐地走向世界
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.91,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.91,0:08:52.83,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.41,0:08:57.75,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅小姐可是会在天国大哭的哦
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.96,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}她又没死！
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.42,0:09:02.42,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这个孩子到底在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.79,0:09:06.42,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个 要不要试试看
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.92,0:09:07.72,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}什么？
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.72,0:09:10.05,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不愧是春乃前辈
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.43,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}要上就上红白
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不是那样的
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.26,0:09:17.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会...我想要不要试试看
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.14,0:09:20.02,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会？为什么
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.98,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么说呢
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.94,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你想啊 不是有已经完成的歌吗
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.19,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.15,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想和大家一起做些什么
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.99,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么 我也算上吗
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.41,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 大家一起
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.74,0:09:36.87,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么样呢
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.42,0:09:48.05,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小的时候经常出现这种情况呢
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.92,0:09:53.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我一个人冲在前面
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.14,0:09:57.10,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}所以我决定了不再逞强
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抱歉不用在心上
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.94,0:10:09.07,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}刚才那些话埋在心里好了
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.86,0:10:12.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今晚还要和大家见面呢...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.82,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真尴尬
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.92,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你好
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.30,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.81,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我是事先预约好的影山
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.37,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我去送野猪汤
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.08,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拜托了
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.08,Default2,Guest,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你要哪个
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.41,Default2,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我想想...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.75,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}晚安
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.04,Default2,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来了来了
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.04,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}晚安
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.59,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}请问春乃呢
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.09,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来一杯咖啡如何
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.38,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.18,0:11:16.80,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这里真是个好地方啊
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢你
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.77,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个是望远镜吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.44,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这个吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.44,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这个叫杜布森望远镜
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.73,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}要看看吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.73,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}可以吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.57,0:11:41.12,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}以为能看见和那张照片上一样的星空吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.12,0:11:41.95,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是的
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.41,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不是那样的吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.41,0:11:47.12,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个是花了很多时间才照下来的哦
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.67,0:11:50.09,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不那样做的话是看不见的
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.25,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}很不可思议吧
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.63,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不拍照吗
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.63,0:12:00.85,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我呢 就这样看着星空 偶尔看看望远镜而已
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.85,0:12:05.52,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我喜欢就这样一边发呆一边想一些事
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.65,0:12:14.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这片夜空中真的有那么多像花朵那么漂亮的星星吗
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.36,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.66,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽然离我们很远很远看不见
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.49,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是慢慢花上一些时间的话就能渐渐地看清
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.58,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不觉得这和人们的内心很像吗
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.58,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}人的内心吗...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.25,0:12:36.63,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}或许我该多花些时间去了解大家的心理吧
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.42,0:12:40.93,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小影 你又在发呆了吗
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.60,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全力发呆中哦 辛西娅
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.60,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你们已经是好朋友了？
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.81,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我把野猪汤带过来了
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.82,0:12:56.78,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大家真的来帮忙了啊
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.53,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}白天的事 不用放在心上哦
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.99,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}突然说了些奇怪的话 抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.75,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个 演唱会打算在哪儿举行呢
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.71,0:13:14.21,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃的话 我们有好好地考虑过
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.21,0:13:17.01,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}难道说武道馆什么的？
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.34,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.76,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就在我家的那个小舞台上
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.68,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叫[Poco a Poco]怎么样
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.43,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}组合的名字
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.85,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一点点来的意思
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.32,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我觉得很好
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.32,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么就开始帮忙吧
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.91,0:13:46.24,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我一直以为无法跨越的沟壑
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}或许并没有我想像的那么巨大
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.71,0:13:54.08,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和大家一起的话 或许我还能更向前走一点
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.71,0:13:58.05,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}慢慢地 慢慢地...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.94,0:14:18.48,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么 开始吧 小影
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.90,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}OK
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.79,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在下前来收蛋了
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来天体观测的影山小姐
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.71,0:14:39.80,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在其他人回家以后也继续住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:46.65,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(484,397)\be1\fad(320,320)}于是开始了 回忆
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.93,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哎 从那时开始一直？
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.39,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 看上去是和辛西娅意气相投
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.76,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}工作没事吗
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.76,0:14:51.43,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 好像是儿童文学的作家 还是挺自由的
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.77,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}作家吗
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.77,0:14:53.81,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是的
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.86,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这么一说 还真感觉有种独特的风格呢
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.95,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poco a Poco!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.70,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那是什么
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.41,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}打招呼啦 组合的
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.75,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}话说 小夜前辈歌词写好了吗
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.50,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}还没
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.42,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}杏里前辈 作曲呢
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.38,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个 还剩最后一点
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.75,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃前辈 唱歌的练习呢
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.38,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没怎么...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.80,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真是的 这样怎么行
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.68,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}要有作为组合的自觉啊
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.35,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.89,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那啥...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.35,0:15:35.39,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没有我能做的事情
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.23,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊 说起来
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.61,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Augh!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.61,0:15:41.61,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没问题的 利绘亲也有事干的
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.15,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎样的
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.36,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这个嘛...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.95,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那经纪人什么的
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.70,0:15:50.83,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}经纪人吗？
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.33,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}合唱
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.12,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再加上铃鼓吧
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.25,Default2,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poco a Poco!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.96,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poco a Poco!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.84,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利绘亲 说实话我对你很期待
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.84,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好吧
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.89,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么大家跟着利绘经纪人一起来吧
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.43,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}加油吧
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.47,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}加油！
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.10,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poco a Poco!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.85,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心情转换得真快啊
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.81,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}放学后去茂登屋开会吧
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.31,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.32,0:16:30.28,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喂喂 已经开始开会了
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.03,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.29,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}人家认真点干啊
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.87,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}干着呢
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.29,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}刚刚旋律在海脑里飘荡呢
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.50,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}美妙的句子即将闪现了
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.38,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}脑内唱歌练习中...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.26,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在说了 演唱会预定什么时候啊
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.30,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}什么时候？
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.52,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明年的春天吧
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.52,0:16:56.10,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就是那时吧
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.39,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}考虑到要有各种准备
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.65,0:17:00.85,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春天啊
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.82,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在那之前能拿到驾照吗
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.46,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个 修好了啊
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.50,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不是说没有零件吗
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.05,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好像是重新制作了的
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.42,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真是好毅力 是我的榜样
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.13,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这样啊
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.13,0:17:35.06,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这个声音是有众多的零件结合在一起的声音呢
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.35,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也是组合
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.52,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}大家团结起来去演唱音乐
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.06,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}说的正是组合
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.28,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么我们也一起启动引擎吧
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.61,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}糟糕 刚才我说的太帅勒
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.53,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}利绘亲很厉害吧
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.53,0:17:55.49,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你们就尽情称颂利绘我吧
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.70,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哎 不在了
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.29,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不亏是利绘亲
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.29,0:18:02.62,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}靠 棒读 太过份了
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.89,0:18:18.47,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不是吧
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.52,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅她？
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.77,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.56,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}本来她来的时候就是有期限的
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.36,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}会变得寂寞呢
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.49,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我才没有...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是利绘亲她们
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.67,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.59,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}购物任务完成
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.59,0:18:52.13,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新的甜点还顺利吗
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.13,0:18:55.22,Default2,Father,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也想啊
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.51,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.93,0:19:03.27,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅 要离开这里了吗
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.31,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 想告诉你来着
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.78,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}演唱会准备春天举办
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.74,0:19:16.82,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}下周六不出发不行呢
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是这样啊
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.84,0:19:33.30,Default2,Cynthia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃你们的歌曲 我听不到了吗
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.30,0:19:38.05,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也不知道 还得问问大家呢
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.57,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真搞不懂
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.45,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果然来了
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.45,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这里还真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.21,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}影山小姐？为什么？
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.71,0:20:12.17,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}听辛西娅说的 可以打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.59,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嗯 请吧
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.68,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真是绝佳地点呢
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.39,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}请问 要喝茶吗
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.06,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.89,0:20:28.02,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅说是要回澳大利亚
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.69,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}出发日期不能延后了
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.69,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是吗
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.69,0:20:40.12,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全世界到处跑 真厉害呢
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.12,0:20:45.12,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是这次回到澳大利亚以后 说是要暂时停止旅行了
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.33,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}别看那么自由 也有很多原因呢
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.84,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}日本的旅途 这里是最后一站吗
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.13,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好像是呢
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.13,0:20:59.89,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么去更好的地方多好
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.64,0:21:05.97,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}说是给我点刺激 虽说是被妈妈拜托的
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.60,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我想辛西娅也是想来才来的
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.73,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是吗
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.77,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃也想应援她对吧
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.61,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.82,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}应援吗
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.82,0:21:23.74,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}[要借助更多 更多的力量]辛西娅说过的
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.74,0:21:27.29,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我想做的事情中有那种价值吗 我都不知道
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.92,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想做的事是唱歌？
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.71,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.55,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那不就行了
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.55,0:21:36.63,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也就那回事吧
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.76,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}什么
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.76,0:21:41.39,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那种暧昧的应援靠不住的啦
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.39,0:21:45.10,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}应援 也不是非要靠得住才行
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.76,0:21:49.02,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只要看到你的努力 就够了
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.02,0:21:51.90,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}应援给她的人自己往往不注意呢
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.90,0:21:56.19,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但就是那种看不见的力量才是最重要的
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.19,0:21:59.19,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}难道说影山小姐你也是？
Dialogue: 5,0:21:59.19,0:22:01.11,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}当然了
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.11,0:22:05.33,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不去借助别人来实现梦想的人是不存在的
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.33,0:22:11.79,Default2,Kageyama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}春乃们的歌去我也想听听看
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.09,0:22:20.13,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}辛西娅小姐
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.38,0:22:24.05,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不哭了 不哭了 我能理解你
Dialogue: 5,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.01,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么办
Dialogue: 5,0:22:27.01,0:22:29.47,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你问我怎么办啊...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.48,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}有什么好烦恼的
Dialogue: 5,0:22:32.27,0:22:33.77,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有去做了呢
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.77,0:22:36.31,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}下周之前完成
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.36,Default2,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那么 先找辛西娅小姐谈谈吧
Dialogue: 5,0:22:38.36,0:22:41.19,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不行 不能依靠辛西娅小姐
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.70,0:22:45.82,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这是我们对辛西娅小姐的报告
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.58,0:22:57.21,Default2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poco a Poco!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.38,0:23:04.63,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我们也点燃了引擎
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.47,0:23:08.14,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}现在的我们打算唱歌
Dialogue: 5,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.60,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那天的会议虽然很热闹
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.60,0:23:13.10,Default2,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谢谢
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.39,0:23:16.81,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但是没有人知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.81,Default2,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喂 这个拿去吧
Dialogue: 5,0:23:17.52,0:23:23.78,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那天起我们不论做什么都在想着歌曲的事
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.57,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}各自做着自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.04,0:23:34.83,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}然后 果然还是听听辛西娅小姐的意思
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.83,0:23:37.83,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}就这样 渐渐地明晰起来了
Dialogue: 5,0:23:40.05,0:23:44.30,Default2,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}虽然总有一天大家会各自离去
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.30,0:23:47.93,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论是十年后 还是二十年后
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.93,0:23:51.56,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一定会回想起现在大家一起创作的歌曲
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.56,0:23:54.14,Default2,Sayo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和这股令人心情愉快的风一起
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.89,0:23:58.77,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}被群山环绕这小小的不方便的小镇
Dialogue: 5,0:23:58.77,0:24:00.23,Default2,Anri,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}毫无内容的杂谈
